      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "The single-pane rollup over the whole DreggNet edge: every service's up/down, the consensus headline, the lease economy, and the durable store. Backed by the blackbox probes + the ops `/api/health` json-exporter.\n\n---\n_New here? See **docs/GRAFANA-GUIDE.md** for how to read each dashboard. The admin portal (ops dashboard) is the human \"what's going on\" view; this board is the deep time-series._"
